description:
A physics student from Japan forming the two-person occult circle, the Secret Seals Club, along with Maribel Hearn. While an inhabitant of the Outside World, she is one of the few humans aware of the Gensokyo`s existence.
She is interested in the paranormal but has a very objective and logical approach to these matters.
She possess the abilities to tell the current time by looking at the stars and the current place by looking at the moon (acting as a human-GPS).
name: Usami Renko
